- Hierarchy: 20–28px headings (600–700), 14–16px card titles (500–600), 12–14px body, 11–12px captions
- Spacing: 8px baseline grid, sidebar ~220–260px, header 56–64px, card padding 16–20px
- Alignments: left-aligned lists in sidebar; mixed grid in main content

Key Design Elements
