- Navigation: left vertical with accent pill on active item; collapsible sections
- Data Visualization: minimal axes, subdued gridlines, colored series, tooltips with small shadows
- Interactive Elements: Primary/Secondary buttons, inputs, toggles, chips; micro-interactions with subtle transitions
- Badges: counts in subdued gray or red accents for alerts

Design Philosophy
- Focused, high-contrast casual-dark UI optimized for productivity
- Dense, tool-heavy interface suitable for power users
- Clear, auditable actions with traceable state changes
- Consistent visual language across plan, calendar, nutrition, and grocery components

Optional Notes
- While no live APIs are connected in this prompt, architect the code with clean separation between UI, domain logic, and data access layers so that real backend services can be plugged in later with minimal changes.
- Ensure the codebase enforces robust runtime safety rules outlined in the Mandatory Coding Standards — especially guarding against null/undefined before using array methods and initializing state with proper defaults.

